The following data is to be used for this question and Qn. 22,23,24.
Mary, a lecturer bought a Disability Income Insurance Policy, became disabled on 30/6/2018. Her details as follows:
Salary: $8,000 per month;
Her expenses: $3,000 per month;
Annual Escalation Benefit: 3%;
6 Month Deferred Period chosen
When will she received the first payment from the insurer and for how much?

